{"tid":1477851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［突發］央視：國泰接受CEO何杲辭職","createTime":"2019-08-16T09:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T09:19:08.000Z","uid":103672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e49446c2592a52e993920fb0edce9999f60eb4af","tid":1477851,"uid":103672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"央視新聞微博發出消息，國泰航空（293）已接受何杲辭任行政總裁職務，將由鄧健榮接替，盧家培辭任顧客及商務總裁職務，由林紹波接替。惟於央視發放消息之際，港交所倘未有任何相關消息公佈。<br />\n<br />\n國泰早前有副機師被捕及被控暴動罪，及後中國民航局上周對國泰發出警示，促使國泰將涉嫌暴動罪的機師停飛，又解僱兩位涉洩警員航班資料的地勤員工。何杲本周一即向員工發放聲明，稱該公司任何時間有義務地遵守法律，指員工支持或參與非法抗議活動將接受紀律處分，後果包括被解僱。<br />\n<br />\n何杲發放的聲明指，對員工們過去兩個月的貢獻及專業表示非常感動，但稱會完全遵守內地民航局上周發出的通知。何杲指出，若抗議活動被視為違法，員工不應支持及參與這種抗議。<br />\n<br />\nSource:【逆權運動】央視：國泰接受CEO何杲辭職<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190816&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59939742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190816%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59939742&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=f9bad390\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190816%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D59939742&h=49e40a52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190816&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=59939742</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知咩事&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebf4cc8c3a59679f7464f0b1eb05544278098b6","tid":1477851,"uid":281926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:17:43.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2nDsML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2nDsML